title: Oregon Geospatial Enterprise Office, Populated Place Names, Oregon, 1990
name: Oregon Geospatial Enterprise Office, Populated Place Names, Oregon, 1990
description:
This point theme shows the location of populated places in the state of Oregon as derived from the 1:24,000 GNIS theme. 
Purpose:
    The purpose of this theme is to delineate the location of populated places in the state of Oregon.

author.source: USGS Geographic Names Information System (GNIS); Oregon Geospatial Enterprise Office
